---
export const prerender = true;
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Nuestra Historia | Eva Torres">
    <Header />
    <main class="bg-eva-dark text-white overflow-x-hidden">

        <section class="relative min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center pt-32 pb-20 px-4">
            
            <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-eva-green rounded-full blur-[120px] opacity-30 pointer-events-none"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-eva-gold rounded-full blur-[120px] opacity-20 pointer-events-none"></div>

            <div class="relative z-10 text-center max-w-5xl mx-auto">
                <span class="text-eva-gold tracking-[0.5em] uppercase text-sm font-bold animate-fade-in opacity-0" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">Desde 2008</span>
                
                <h1 class="font-heading text-6xl md:text-8xl lg:text-9xl leading-none mt-6 mb-12 opacity-0 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
                    Pasión <span class="italic text-eva-gold font-serif">&</span> Alma
                </h1>

                <div class="relative inline-block group opacity-0 animate-scale-in" style="animation-delay: 0.8s;">
                    <div class="absolute -inset-4 border border-eva-gold/30 rounded-sm scale-95 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700 ease-out"></div>
                    
                    <div class="relative overflow-hidden w-full max-w-md mx-auto shadow-2xl shadow-black/50 rounded-sm">
                        <img 
                            src="https://imgur.com/ISYXi1A.jpg" 
                            alt="Interior Tienda Eva Torres" 
                            class="w-full h-auto object-cover transform transition-transform duration-1000 group-hover:scale-110"
                        >
                        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-eva-dark/40 to-transparent mix-blend-overlay"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <p class="mt-12 text-xl md:text-2xl font-light text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed opacity-0 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 1.2s;">
                    En el corazón de Arahal, creamos un espacio donde la moda cobra vida y el trato humano es la única tendencia que nunca pasa.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce opacity-50">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6 text-eva-gold">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 8.25l-7.5 7.5-7.5-7.5" />
                </svg>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="py-32 bg-white text-eva-dark relative">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
                
                <div class="space-y-24">
                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-8">
                        <div class="md:w-1/3 text-eva-gold font-brand text-6xl opacity-80 sticky top-32">
                            01.
                        </div>
                        <div class="md:w-2/3">
                            <h3 class="text-4xl font-heading mb-6">El Comienzo</h3>
                            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed font-light">
                                En la <strong>Barriada Francisco de Quevedo</strong>, Eva Torres abrió sus puertas no solo como una tienda, sino como una declaración de intenciones. Queríamos demostrar que el comercio de barrio podía ofrecer la misma exclusividad y calidad que las grandes boutiques de la capital, pero con la calidez de quien te saluda por tu nombre.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="w-full h-px bg-gray-200"></div>

                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-8">
                        <div class="md:w-1/3 text-eva-gold font-brand text-6xl opacity-80 sticky top-32">
                            02.
                        </div>
                        <div class="md:w-2/3">
                            <h3 class="text-4xl font-heading mb-6">La Evolución</h3>
                            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed font-light">
                                Escuchar es nuestro secreto. Cada prenda que ves en nuestros percheros está ahí porque alguna vez nos contaste qué necesitabas. Crecimos de ser una zapatería a ofrecer looks completos, porque entendimos que la elegancia es un conjunto, una actitud, y queríamos acompañarte en todo el proceso.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="py-32 bg-eva-cream relative overflow-hidden">

            <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-16 lg:gap-24">

                    <div class="md:w-1/2 relative group">
                        <div class="absolute -left-12 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-[12rem] lg:text-[18rem] font-heading text-white font-bold leading-none select-none pointer-events-none opacity-60 z-0 transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:translate-x-4">
                            EVA
                        </div>

                        <div class="absolute inset-0 border-2 border-eva-gold/20 translate-x-4 translate-y-4 z-0 transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:translate-x-2 group-hover:translate-y-2"></div>

                        <div class="relative z-10 overflow-hidden rounded-sm shadow-2xl">
                            <img 
                                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1496747611176-843222e1e57c?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" 
                                alt="Detalle Moda Elegante Eva Torres" 
                                class="w-full h-[600px] object-cover grayscale-[10%] group-hover:grayscale-0 group-hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-700 ease-out"
                            >
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="md:w-1/2 text-left">
                        <div class="max-w-xl">
                            <h2 class="text-eva-gold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-bold mb-8 text-sm flex items-center gap-4">
                                <span class="w-12 h-px bg-eva-gold"></span> Nuestra Filosofía
                            </h2>
                            <p class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-heading text-eva-dark leading-tight mb-10">
                                "La moda no es sobre la ropa. Es sobre <span class="text-eva-green italic relative inline-block">la mujer<span class="absolute bottom-2 left-0 w-full h-3 bg-eva-gold/20 -z-10"></span></span> que la lleva."
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg font-light mb-12 leading-relaxed">
                                Creemos en el poder de sentirte segura. Por eso, nuestro asesoramiento va más allá de la talla; buscamos conectar con tu estilo de vida y resaltar tu belleza natural.
                            </p>
                            <a href="/contacto" class="group inline-flex items-center gap-4 bg-eva-dark text-white px-10 py-4 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs font-bold hover:bg-eva-gold transition-all shadow-xl rounded-sm">
                                <span>Ven a conocernos</span>
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">
                                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.25 8.25L21 12m0 0l-3.75 3.75M21 12H3" />
                                </svg>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

    </main>
    <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
    /* Animaciones CSS personalizadas */
    .animate-fade-in { animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out forwards; }
    .animate-fade-in-up { animation: fadeInUp 1s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1) forwards; }
    .animate-scale-in { animation: scaleIn 1.2s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1) forwards; }

    @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; } to { opacity: 1; } }
    @keyframes fadeInUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(40px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
    @keyframes scaleIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.9); filter: blur(10px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); filter: blur(0); } }
</style>